  "用 Path(...).glob('*.txt') 遍历目录，收集所有 .txt 文件并打印数量。": "Use Path(...).glob('*.txt') to walk a directory, collect every .txt file and print the count.",
  "Path('.').glob('*.txt') 返回一个生成器，用 for 循环逐个取出 Path 对象。": "Path('.').glob('*.txt') returns a generator; iterate it with a for loop to get each Path object.",
