  "pandas 读得快，openpyxl 控得细": "pandas reads fast, openpyxl controls fine",
  "如果只是把数据原样存成 Excel，df.to_excel 一行就够。但真实报表往往要表头加粗、列宽、合并、公式、颜色——这些 pandas 管不了。openpyxl 直接操作工作簿对象：一个 Workbook 里有多张 Worksheet，每张表由单元格组成。需要排版控制时，就用它。": "If you only need to dump data into Excel as-is, df.to_excel in one line is enough. But real reports often need bold headers, column widths, merges, formulas, colors—pandas can't do those. openpyxl operates on the workbook object directly: a Workbook holds multiple Worksheets, each made of cells. When you need layout control, reach for it.",
  "Workbook() 自带一张 active 表": "Workbook() comes with one active sheet",
  "append 逐行写，单元格按 A1 定位": "append writes rows; cells are addressed like A1",
  "最省事的写法是 ws.append(行)，它把一个序列写到当前最后一行的下方。写完后想精修某个单元格，就用 Excel 那套坐标：ws[\"A1\"] 是第一行第一列，ws[\"B2\"] 是第二行第二列。坐标既能读值也能设样式。": "The easiest way is ws.append(row), which writes a sequence below the current last row. To fine-tune a specific cell afterward, use Excel-style coordinates: ws[\"A1\"] is row 1 column 1, ws[\"B2\"] is row 2 column 2. Coordinates can both read values and set styles.",
  "append 逐行写入，A1 坐标读值": "append writes row by row; A1 coordinates read values",
  "append 接受元组或列表，元素顺序就是从左到右的列顺序。": "append takes a tuple or list; element order is the left-to-right column order.",
  "样式与保存": "Styling and saving",
  "样式不是直接改值，而是给单元格的属性赋一个样式对象。加粗用 Font(bold=True)，赋给 cell.font。表头通常多列，逐个设就行。最后一定要 wb.save(路径)——openpyxl 全程在内存里操作，不 save 就什么都没落盘，而且扩展名要写 .xlsx。": "Styling isn't changing the value; it's assigning a style object to a cell attribute. Bold is Font(bold=True), assigned to cell.font. A header usually spans several columns, so set each one. Finally you must wb.save(path)—openpyxl works entirely in memory, and nothing hits disk until you save; use the .xlsx extension.",
  "遍历首行加粗，再保存为 .xlsx": "Bold the whole first row, then save as .xlsx",
