  "从 PDF 提取文本": "Extract text from a PDF",
  "读取": "Read",
  "用 pdfplumber.open 打开 PDF，遍历每一页调用 extract_text()，把各页文本拼接到一个字符串里。": "Open a PDF with pdfplumber.open, loop over every page calling extract_text(), and join each page's text into one string.",
  "用 with pdfplumber.open(path) as pdf: 保证文件被正确关闭。": "Use with pdfplumber.open(path) as pdf: so the file is closed properly.",
  "pdf.pages 是页面列表，for page in pdf.pages 逐页处理。": "pdf.pages is a list of pages; for page in pdf.pages processes them one by one.",
  "extract_text() 在空白页或纯图片页会返回 None，先判断再 append。": "extract_text() returns None on blank or image-only pages, so check before you append.",
  "用 pdfplumber.open 打开": "Open with pdfplumber.open",
  "用 pdfplumber.open(path) 打开 PDF。": "Open the PDF with pdfplumber.open(path).",
  "遍历 pdf.pages": "Loop over pdf.pages",
  "用 for page in pdf.pages 逐页遍历。": "Use for page in pdf.pages to iterate the pages.",
  "调用 extract_text()": "Call extract_text()",
  "对每页调用 page.extract_text() 取文本。": "Call page.extract_text() on each page to get its text.",
  "处理 None 空页": "Handle None pages",
  "extract_text 可能返回 None，用 if 或 or \"\" 兜底再拼接。": "extract_text may return None; guard with an if or or \"\" before joining.",
  "PDF 不是表格，是排版": "A PDF is layout, not a table",
  "发票、合同、对账单经常只发 PDF。PDF 里没有「行列」概念，只有文字在页面上的坐标，所以提取出来的是一团带换行的纯文本，需要你后续再用字符串或正则去切。pdfplumber 是目前对中文和表格定位最友好的库之一，入口就是 pdfplumber.open。": "Invoices, contracts, and statements often arrive only as PDF. A PDF has no concept of rows and columns—only the coordinates of text on the page—so what you extract is a blob of newline-laden plain text that you must later slice with strings or regex. pdfplumber is one of the friendliest libraries for Chinese text and table positioning, and the entry point is pdfplumber.open.",
  "open 后 pdf.pages 给出页数": "After open, pdf.pages gives the page count",
  "扫描件（图片型 PDF）提不出文字，那需要 OCR，不在本课范围。": "Scanned (image-based) PDFs yield no text and need OCR, which is out of scope here.",
  "逐页提取，逐页累积": "Extract page by page, accumulate page by page",
  "pdf.pages 是页面对象的列表，标准做法是 for 遍历，每页调用 extract_text() 拿到该页文本。别想着一次性取全文——库的接口就是按页的。把每页结果收集到一个 list，最后用 \"\\n\".join 拼成整篇，比反复字符串相加高效得多。": "pdf.pages is a list of page objects; the standard approach is a for loop, calling extract_text() on each page to get that page's text. Don't expect a whole-document call—the API is page-based. Collect each page's result into a list and join with \"\\n\".join at the end, far more efficient than repeated string concatenation.",
  "逐页 extract_text 收进列表": "extract_text per page, collected in a list",
  "空页会返回 None，必须兜底": "Blank pages return None, you must guard",
  "这是最容易踩的坑：空白页或纯图片页，extract_text() 返回的是 None 而不是空字符串。直接把 None 丢进 \"\\n\".join 会抛 TypeError。要么 if text: 再 append，要么用 text or \"\" 兜底成空串。处理外部文件，永远假设它会给你意料之外的东西。": "This is the classic trap: on a blank or image-only page, extract_text() returns None, not an empty string. Feeding None into \"\\n\".join raises a TypeError. Either guard with if text: before appending, or fall back with text or \"\". When handling external files, always assume they'll hand you something unexpected.",
  "用 or \"\" 把 None 变成安全的空串": "Turn None into a safe empty string with or \"\"",
  "别假设每页都有文字——一个 None 就能让整段拼接崩掉。": "Don't assume every page has text—a single None can crash the whole join.",
